{"tid":1603644,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"寫咗個Javascript一鍵製作大量海報","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T09:57:40.000Z","uid":138868,"like":234,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"e61484ace0222e8a3fcde51e6e570a967df28d38","tid":1603644,"uid":138868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1390893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1390893/page/1</a><br />\n上次用Java轉exe<br />\n今次改用Javascript希望易用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以揀File同埋中途改資料<br />\n<br />\n差唔多選學生會／海報，應該好多人要整一堆設計差唔多但內容唔同嘅海報，但逐張改真係好麻煩<br />\n<br />\n圖放images folder<br />\n拉個excel入去<br />\nCheck下個excel仲有冇嘢要改<br />\n拉埋海報個Config入去<br />\n自動跟ID gen一堆海報出嚟<br />\ndownload完放返入result folder<br />\n唔知點解有時會down多咗幾個html.txt, 我估關個excel事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHPAtXV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHPAtXV.gif&h=df1c75c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bNdahRo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbNdahRo.gif&h=3be562e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nID = file名<br />\n如果excel入面嗰格冇嘢, html會自動隱藏<br />\n如果有QR code會出現喺右下角<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n範例<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBgnTqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBgnTqh.png&h=6ac2ea07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8azHTpS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8azHTpS.png&h=5aca6562&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eK4s4wx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeK4s4wx.png&h=80994c78&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nTTahRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnTTahRy.png&h=25fab4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壊處係新設計/改版面要寫css, 同埋度位都幾撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec65bfec44300ab944c83d73b956c24b57c1704","tid":1603644,"uid":49943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa351f52c06a53a62371e241a1702244cd013248","tid":1603644,"uid":322326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一推,有用 post"},{"pid":"1f76e236bb39e4a1467db8c5ce7481de7ef64997","tid":1603644,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38802ae4ddd519f5e048b3fc3edf870e75111b1","tid":1603644,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7687d326f69697464f5a2a4fd082dfc2869cd327","tid":1603644,"uid":137992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6b1a9aa3261612c614043c5024345b531c05e027","tid":1603644,"uid":138868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ffdf3786b01cd640a1bddce80b97e457820c89","tid":1603644,"uid":138868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi